	<description>
		POWO draws together Kew’s extensive data resources including its regional Floras and
		monographs, alongside images from the digitisation of the collections. The portal
		has been designed to maximise accessibility and enables the dissemination of plant
		information to its users via a mobile, tablet or desktop computer.
	</description>

